      "role": "user",
      "content": "i moved halfway across the world to start over and i feel like i'm just... a ghost. like i walk through these streets and if i just stopped existing tomorrow, the city wouldn't even skip a beat. no one even knows my name here. it's like i'm not even really part of the world.",
